SURF_INTOX
www.intoxGaming.com

Noob end - Deagle in jail spawn.
Pro end - Jail gas, M4A1 above jail, kill buttons.
Secret end 1 - Deagle in jail spawn.
Secret end 2 - Controllable turret next to jail, awp, free button, kill buttons.

Hints:
When you're falling down the hole after the bunny hopping make sure the red triangle is at the bottom left corner of your screen and you're holding down D.

Credits:
Japetheape

FYI. For some reason the screenshots look alot darker than the map actually is. Feedback & CC are welcome.
